me":"2016-12-23T05:11:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n樓主哥哥求linux<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 5連</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實上面我講左隻OS名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nKorora 25 Gnome 版</blockquote><br />\n除左wine同裝多隻windows<br />\n有無更好方法搞掂個相容</blockquote><br />\n<br />\ndual boot<br />\n我隻Windows 10都係畫圖先會boot入去"},{"pid":"22e1499f3fc1ea3818ad1ac877ef368e5d31f707","tid":50654,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T05:31:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>先貼為敬<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/94YJ8i8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F94YJ8i8.jpg&h=df071498&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nLinux都可以好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓主哥哥求linux<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />4連</blockquote><br />\n樓主哥哥求linux<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 5連</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實上面我講左隻OS名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nKorora 25 Gnome 版</blockquote><br />\n除左wine同裝多隻windows<br />\n有無更好方法搞掂個相容</blockquote><br />\nwine、multi-boot、vm效果都係唔理想，如果想用返MS Windows的軟件，最好都係唔好裝Linux，繼續用返MS Windows</blockquote><br />\nvm效果好理想喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6612a52f0658f2952fa75bb754b1528a85add51","tid":50654,"uid":13533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:11:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實上面我講左隻OS名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nKorora 25 Gnome 版</blockquote><br />\n除左wine同裝多隻windows<br />\n有無更好方法搞掂個相容</blockquote><br />\nwine、multi-boot、vm效果都係唔理想，如果想用返MS Windows的軟件，最好都係唔好裝Linux，繼續用返MS Windows</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認真 你坐咗幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da1c1029ad7e2c6fd28a8a98886428d09203388b","tid":50654,"uid":23904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T09:00:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實上面我講左隻OS名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nKorora 25 Gnome 版</blockquote><br />\n除左wine同裝多隻windows<br />\n有無更好方法搞掂個相容</blockquote><br />\n<br />\ndual boot<br />\n我隻Windows 10都係畫圖先會boot入去</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果想korora windows dual boot <br />\n係咪2 個os 分開hd?"},{"pid":"7b7c8cd8eebe6ca1f1701a8e9bb33c08e83e9831","tid":50654,"uid":53857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T09:05:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n除左wine同裝多隻windows<br />\n有無更好方法搞掂個相容</blockquote><br />\n<br />\ndual boot<br />\n我隻Windows 10都係畫圖先會boot入去</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果想korora windows dual boot <br />\n係咪2 個os 分開hd?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同一隻HDD裝、裝完修復BOOT Loader<br />\n分開hdd裝就無影響，korora boot loader 可以比你選擇boot korora 定boot返入windows"},{"pid":"db4454122337f167360fe180cfb9de7ba4376913","tid":50654,"uid":13391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T09:33:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n除左wine同裝多隻windows<br />\n有無更好方法搞掂個相容</blockquote><br />\nwine、multi-boot、vm效果都係唔理想，如果想用返MS Windows的軟件，最好都係唔好裝Linux，繼續用返MS Windows</blockquote><br />\nvm效果好理想喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nWine又好、vm又好<br />\n最後都係用番Windows<br />\n<br />\n叫做用過Linux咁多年 我覺得如果離唔開Windows嘅<br />\n都係唔好轉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：已轉Mac"},{"pid":"eede1a60d3735ffe561c588892ad2a45dbf673ef","tid":50654,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T10:43:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n除左wine同裝多隻windows<br />\n有無更好方法搞掂個相容</blockquote><br />\nwine、multi-boot、vm效果都係唔理想，如果想用返MS Windows的軟件，最好都係唔好裝Linux，繼續用返MS Windows</blockquote><br />\nvm效果好理想喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nWine又好、vm又好<br />\n最後都係用番Windows<br />\n<br />\n叫做用過Linux咁多年 我覺得如果離唔開Windows嘅<br />\n都係唔好轉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：已轉Mac</blockquote><br />\n幾日都唔開一次，開一次windows只為打機<br />\n同埋，windows既功能(btrfs)、性能(blender)同安全性(唔撚洗講啦)同linux差太遠，我好難日常會轉返用windows<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"036fd39d18505523253c8c1bc139e55607f4f166","tid":50654,"uid":23904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T13:47:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\ndual boot<br />\n我隻Windows 10都係畫圖先會boot入去</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果想korora windows dual boot <br />\n係咪2 個os 分開hd?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同一隻HDD裝、裝完修復BOOT Loader<br />\n分開hdd裝就無影響，korora boot loader 可以比你選擇boot korora 定boot返入windows</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果想分開hdd 裝<br />\n拆左有windows 果個 hdd  跟住裝korora <br />\n之後先插番佢 咁得唔得？"},{"pid":"7298aa27d571d8538ae0bcca020e74c4ffeb49e4","tid":50654,"uid":53857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T14:43:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果想korora windows dual boot <br />\n係咪2 個os 分開hd?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同一隻HDD裝、裝完修復BOOT Loader<br />\n分開hdd裝就無影響，korora boot loader 可以比你選擇boot korora 定boot返入windows</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果想分開hdd 裝<br />\n拆左有windows 果個 hdd  跟住裝korora <br />\n之後先插番佢 咁得唔得？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n得<br />\n不過我裝個時插住黎裝都無問題，但記得裝korora個時set返岩要裝個隻HDD就得"},{"pid":"54d14ebcdf60fff465cb1a85c7e3dc1b9c7df14d","tid":50654,"uid":36035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T16:09:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"533b0ea8d02245880cb7ce4009b2a7a535210d24","tid":50654,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T02:48:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>#37深夜情色園<br />\n<br />\n#38千歳様<br />\n<br />\n係，樓上兩位講得啱，家陣d人好有it經驗，好得閒，搞一大輪個qemu-kvm去玩vm<br />\n<br />\nqemu-kvm好似要兩張顯示卡兩個mon，同粒CPU要support VT-D，之前有人話一張核顯一張顯示卡都得，以及可以一個mon兩個input取代兩個mon，不過始終都係麻鬼煩<br />\n<br />\n唔好老點d新人裝Linux，對於用慣用熟，中意打機的人黎講，MS Windows始終是最好的。我平時唔打機，日日上hkg、lihkg所以先用Linux，我係single boot debian unstable codename sid，而且冇乜點掂VM及wine</blockquote><br />\n嘻"},{"pid":"74d3b6eb750738a016992d25a6bf786015440efe","tid":50654,"uid":15471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T04:52:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/uCjfgiteDAI/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FuCjfgiteDAI%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=32c348ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5fc8619a480d3fc4b16136f64a1210098505fa89","tid":50654,"uid":3952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T09:21:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/24/172124_61d73ec45967035467d5417b6b33da51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F24%2F172124_61d73ec45967035467d5417b6b33da51.jpg&h=d374d752&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2a1c8e5c12124d306abf589968cbb8590e4c52da","tid":50654,"uid":5079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-07T00:28:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u97Ua4v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu97Ua4v.jpg&h=f501465d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dbbb4aa553c0baf91f9edaed326ae11cd970ec12","tid":50654,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-07T06:29:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1oV6iOQ.png