 src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n長期唔明點解 D 人個桌面可以咁亂"},{"pid":"c421f4635f64bf392854b8086465a90cae1b07c9","tid":50654,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T03:36:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1oV6iOQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1oV6iOQ.png&h=91b578e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係咪得我一個係咁亂?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用埋晒 D 垃圾中國軟件</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個windows應該都係老翻嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n長期唔明點解 D 人個桌面可以咁亂</blockquote><br />\n睇到眼都花，呢啲多數懶人嚟"},{"pid":"df4189c89b2a8d6d6c758021377f707bcf9a54aa","tid":50654,"uid":33511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T11:58:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://more-sky.com/WDF-336305.html\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmore-sky.com%2FWDF-336305.html&h=bd29efa5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e13eb0b2b8cc5d494ed86bdfa95a643c124e7d46","tid":50654,"uid":33511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T11:59:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://more-sky.com/data/out/9/IMG_336305.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmore-sky.com%2Fdata%2Fout%2F9%2FIMG_336305.jpg&h=aaef532a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9c0805fbdc5035a43e92adac13d4e6f9a55a5b7d","tid":50654,"uid":33511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T12:02:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://imgur.com/a/RPWiV\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2Fa%2FRPWiV&h=2f4af457&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5eabb960520f9c78b7faf6ffe3cc285efd00e380","tid":50654,"uid":33511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T12:06:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/CBSJqR1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FCBSJqR1.png&h=7dfaa3dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屌原來唔記得login imgur<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84dd32c8f32b225556f52e3e5e4f7ba063650fd9","tid":50654,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T00:38:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>#37深夜情色園<br />\n<br />\n#38千歳様<br />\n<br />\n係，樓上兩位講得啱，家陣d人好有it經驗，好得閒，搞一大輪個qemu-kvm去玩vm<br />\n<br />\nqemu-kvm好似要兩張顯示卡兩個mon，同粒CPU要support VT-D，之前有人話一張核顯一張顯示卡都得，以及可以一個mon兩個input取代兩個mon，不過始終都係麻鬼煩<br />\n<br />\n唔好老點d新人裝Linux，對於用慣用熟，中意打機的人黎講，MS Windows始終是最好的。我平時唔打機，日日上hkg、lihkg所以先用Linux，我係single boot debian unstable codename sid，而且冇乜點掂VM及wine</blockquote><br />\n講得啱，睇到貓叉段kvm打機片，見到佢用到依依唉唉咁嘅聲就知好撚麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa045e012e12932b49d31f20b9b21651800ad8ed","tid":50654,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T01:13:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>#37深夜情色園<br />\n<br />\n#38千歳様<br />\n<br />\n係，樓上兩位講得啱，家陣d人好有it經驗，好得閒，搞一大輪個qemu-kvm去玩vm<br />\n<br />\nqemu-kvm好似要兩張顯示卡兩個mon，同粒CPU要support VT-D，之前有人話一張核顯一張顯示卡都得，以及可以一個mon兩個input取代兩個mon，不過始終都係麻鬼煩<br />\n<br />\n唔好老點d新人裝Linux，對於用慣用熟，中意打機的人黎講，MS Windows始終是最好的。我平時唔打機，日日上hkg、lihkg所以先用Linux，我係single boot debian unstable codename sid，而且冇乜點掂VM及wine</blockquote><br />\n講得啱，睇到貓叉段kvm打機片，見到佢用到依依唉唉咁嘅聲就知好撚麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我最近發現唔洗用mon掣都可以轉mon input<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63a015a08caafa28e87712c6ec020a5f8d7f7e95","tid":50654,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T01:40:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>#37深夜情色園<br />\n<br />\n#38千歳様<br />\n<br />\n係，樓上兩位講得啱，家陣d人好有it經驗，好得閒，搞一大輪個qemu-kvm去玩vm<br />\n<br />\nqemu-kvm好似要兩張顯示卡兩個mon，同粒CPU要support VT-D，之前有人話一張核顯一張顯示卡都得，以及可以一個mon兩個input取代兩個mon，不過始終都係麻鬼煩<br />\n<br />\n唔好老點d新人裝Linux，對於用慣用熟，中意打機的人黎講，MS Windows始終是最好的。我平時唔打機，日日上hkg、lihkg所以先用Linux，我係single boot debian unstable codename sid，而且冇乜點掂VM及wine</blockquote><br />\n講得啱，睇到貓叉段kvm打機片，見到佢用到依依唉唉咁嘅聲就知好撚麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我最近發現唔洗用mon掣都可以轉mon input<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n留名學嘢"},{"pid":"4863e911052c4e822bcab3f1d4f05005ca0835ef","tid":50654,"uid":68290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T10:19:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4Xf2U1g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Xf2U1g.png&h=c2e0987f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n毒撚踩場唔好意思"},{"pid":"819ace80b78d79631d9ba7ba126f430730367c07","tid":50654,"uid":43178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T12:54:26.000Z","msg":"點解你地個桌面咁亂？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dys11zZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdys11zZ.png&h=1c594203&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2af7e742881ce59590730d31d3cf594198ff3739","tid":50654,"uid":24200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T13:03:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1oV6iOQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1oV6iOQ.png&h=91b578e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係咪得我一個係咁亂?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/12/210300_994dbc6dd3314dd64600d01e30785e98.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F12%2F210300_994dbc6dd3314dd64600d01e30785e98.jpg&h=b34c4143&s={SIZE}\" />鹹片？"}]}